      "description": "Hey there! Honestly, I\u2019m so sad to let this beauty go. It is absolutely flawless\u2014seriously, it looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, keeping it garage-kept and sparkling clean. It drives like a dream and is in such incredible shape, you really have to see it to believe it. Feel free to reach out with any questions or if you want to come take it for a spin. I\u2019m sure the first person to see it will fall in love!",
