    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is a true collector-grade vehicle, maintained with an almost obsessive level of care. The exterior features its original factory paint, which has been preserved under a multi-stage paint correction and a premium ceramic coating, resulting in a deep, glass-like finish free of any swirl marks or rock chips. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather upholstery retains its factory matte finish and 'new car' scent, with zero bolster wear or creasing. Every electronic component, from the adaptive cruise control to the climate-controlled seats, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car is peerless, backed by a comprehensive binder of service records documenting every fluid change and preventative maintenance milestone. It has been strictly garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen inclement weather. This isn't just a used car; it\u2019s a pristine example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
